{"pid":"2e7e90a5ac9478f311afc3d1b07250704c1bfe1a","tid":2492334,"uid":118286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b1c8fc7f5acec85301f5fd0d8f539a458b6c357f","tid":2492334,"uid":184103,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:43:14.000Z","msg":"ching平時係咪成日覺得自己好醒嗰啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:38:42.000Z","msg":"React點解唔係library"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T06:43:29.000Z","msg":"可能佢想問得再specific啲<br />\n可能係用人哋components<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話 decompile佢咪知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T06:48:52.000Z","msg":"擺明係懶撚咩都唔識又想搵現成component/npm package"},{"pid":"9d63d5ae7804211226156970ae70a62bc25180b5","tid":2492334,"uid":162421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"自己試吓整再放上黎問唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c38131eb5af786783165b6852cbdab2adb097f","tid":2492334,"uid":9248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"你唔需要 animation 嘅話<br />\n一兩個鐘都整到七八成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae609b212399762f702165e23975478e151462fd","tid":2492334,"uid":9248,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:58:00.000Z","msg":"至於打包 全部 logic 喺晒 server <br />\n<br />\n半 naive implementation 會係咁：<br />\n<br />\n1. User 出 post/comment <br />\n2. Get all image links from the content<br />\n3. insert to database (post_id, image_link), image link should be de-duplicated<br />\n3. Client calls 打包 link<br />\n4. Server get all all image links of post<br />\n5. Generate a cache key (e.g. hash(post_id, array of image_links))<br />\n6. Check if the zip file already exist (in S3, or equivalent, or can also store the generated cached key in database so no need to call 3rd party<br />\n7. If exist, return download link<br />\n8. If not exist, generate the zip in real time.<br />\n9. Store in S3<br />\n10. Return download link to user<br />\n<br />\n最需要 optimise 係 step8<br />\n如果 user request download 先 generate zip file 可能會好慢 <br />\n<br />\n2個 quick solutions<br />\n1. step3之後就 generate zip file. 但會嘥咗好多 resources 去gen 一啲無人 download 過嘅打包<br />\n2. Step 7, 10 唔直接 return download link. Instead, enqueue background job 然後用 long polling 或者 websocket 去等結果"},{"pid":"ba9713f251f02603e5bd35b5d1c1f251894dc2a6","tid":2492334,"uid":52509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"825dc2389218345e17f41aeb63f84415b97ef7d7","tid":2492334,"uid":152643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0017d18a2a526917eed087016f575a351316d6c","tid":2492334,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"bootstrap都整到<br />\n禁制 -&gt; call api 拎個post有咩圖 -&gt; 用popup loop呢堆圖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:33:39.000Z","msg":"而家聯登api仲可唔可以fetch到連登backend嘅嘢？<br />\n定係要再諗其他方法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T11:53:22.000Z","msg":"佢禁咗"},{"pid":"826da57c0e584f8b7242223529789ecbae312a89","tid":2492334,"uid":152643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56c38131eb5af786783165b6852cbdab2adb097f","tid":2492334,"uid":9248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"你唔需要 animation 嘅話<br />\n一兩個鐘都整到七八成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:07:35.000Z","msg":"俾你簡backend會點整？例如用咗thymeleaf, 你會用expression language將啲圖塞落html node到，定唔塞落去？"},{"pid":"b13b7a571acd585f491342fb59abfab90d97d0e1","tid":2492334,"uid":152643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae609b212399762f702165e23975478e151462fd","tid":2492334,"uid":9248,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:58:00.000Z","msg":"至於打包 全部 logic 喺晒 server <br />\n<br />\n半 naive implementation 會係咁：<br />\n<br />\n1. User 出 post/comment <br />\n2. Get all image links from the content<br />\n3. insert to database (post_id, image_link), image link should be de-duplicated<br />\n3. Client calls 打包 link<br />\n4. Server get all all image links of post<br />\n5. Generate a cache key (e.g. hash(post_id, array of image_links))<br />\n6. Check if the zip file already exist (in S3, or equivalent, or can also store the generated cached key in database so no need to call 3rd party<br />\n7. If exist, return download link<br />\n8. If not exist, generate the zip in real time.<br />\n9. Store in S3<br />\n10. Return download link to user<br />\n<br />\n最需要 optimise 係 step8<br />\n如果 user request download 先 generate zip file 可能會好慢 <br />\n<br />\n2個 quick solutions<br />\n1. step3之後就 generate zip file. 但會嘥咗好多 resources 去gen 一啲無人 download 過嘅打包<br />\n2. Step 7, 10 唔直接 return download link. Instead, enqueue background job 然後用 long polling 或者 websocket 去等結果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:10:32.000Z","msg":"將zipped file放入db table係咪比較少見？因為可能大過2mb?s3係類似file system定db table?"},{"pid":"e0b5c46be82b77097e921dcaf08431a6ab68cd5d","tid":2492334,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"826da57c0e584f8b7242223529789ecbae312a89","tid":2492334,"uid":152643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56c38131eb5af786783165b6852cbdab2adb097f","tid":2492334,"uid":9248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"你唔需要 animation 嘅話<br />\n一兩個鐘都整到七八成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:07:35.000Z","msg":"俾你簡backend會點整？例如用咗thymeleaf, 你會用expression language將啲圖塞落html node到，定唔塞落去？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:12:51.000Z","msg":"Amazon S3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as